                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Dirty leaf-lover!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->I'll gnaw on your [BodyPart]!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Touch some concrete, disgusting treehugger!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Goddamn knife-ear!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->This is for my underlord!</li>
