                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->I can smell your fear!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->You and your people will die!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Come here, disgusting [INITIATOR_alienRace]!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Diggy diggy skull!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->I was forged to kill!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->I'll mine you like slate!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Your mother would be ashamed!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Fight me!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Is that all you got, slag?!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Do you hug your mother with those weak arms?!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->I am a proud [INITIATOR_kind]!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->For [INITIATOR_factionName]!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Die by the [INITIATOR_WEAPON_label] of [INITIATOR_nameFull]!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->You're puny, dreg!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Scrawnier than a gnoblin's arms!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Skinnier than an elf!</li>
                <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Where is your fighting spirit?!</li>
