              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->For the forge!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->For Grugni!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Just come here, it'll all be over soon!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->This could be a lot simpler!</li>
