              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->No escape!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->It's killed or be killed, and I'm not planning on dying!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->I'm [AdjectiveBadass]!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Hope you enjoyed having a functioning [BodyPart]!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Die, die die!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->I'm unstoppable!</li>
              <li>rule(Dwarven_Callouts==true,p=1000)->Let's show them what's what!</li>
